        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Road to Recovery Act</b></p> <p>This bill provides for coverage, under Medicaid&nbsp;and the Children's Health Insurance Program (CHIP), of inpatient services in a residential substance-use disorder treatment facility with respect to an individual under 65 years of age.</p>]]></text>
